{"tid":968234,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"認愛5個月！泫雅甜喊白粉仔E'Dawn「3個字」","createTime":"2019-01-04T05:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T10:20:22.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"38a33d80bc32d0a8b1fcbb914fdeec3532a1ed44","tid":968234,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:36:32.000Z","msg":"南韓女星泫雅公開認愛師弟E'Dawn（金曉鐘）後，越愛越大方，不僅常在社群網站上公開放閃，<span style=\"color: red;\">她4日PO出兩人合作的新歌影片，更直接稱呼對方為「未婚夫」，掀起熱烈討論。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3809/3809941.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3809%2F3809941.jpg&h=372b2c94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3809/3809939.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3809%2F3809939.jpg&h=80af5ae8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泫雅和E'Dawn交往2年。（圖／翻攝自IG／泫雅）<br />\n<br />\n泫雅4日曬出一段影片，只見畫面中，她和男友E'Dawn並肩坐在椅子上，疑似正聽著兩人合作的新歌，她並在IG上PO出歌詞：「那種細微的差別只有我們知道，所有的一切我都願意承諾，我的Fianc&eacute;（未婚夫），你和我走在相同的路上，一起度過剩下的時間。」直接稱呼男友為未婚夫。網友看了紛紛驚呼：「這是什麼情況」、「好事將近了嗎」、「希望有好結果」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3809/d3809938.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3809%2Fd3809938.jpg&h=d4ac9a0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3809/d3809937.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3809%2Fd3809937.jpg&h=0d8c88a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泫雅疑將與E'Dawn合作新歌。（圖／翻攝自IG／泫雅）<br />\n泫雅2018年8月被爆熱戀師弟E&rsquo;Dawn，起初經紀公司否認，但隨即遭當事人打臉，並承認已交往2年多，因公司和兩人的說法反覆，引起粉絲反彈，E&rsquo;Dawn遭暫時停止活動，隨後9月中爆出Cube娛樂以「無法恢復信任」為由，決定將兩人退社，最後雙方在10月中與11月中與經紀公司解除合約，打包離開。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3809/d3809940.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3809%2Fd3809940.jpg&h=6328ec73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泫雅與師弟E'Dawn認愛後，雙雙被公司辭退。（圖／翻攝自IG／泫雅）<br />\n<br />\n【泫雅IG發文】<br />\n那種細微的差別只有我們知道<br />\n所有的一切我都願意承諾 Fianc&eacute;<br />\n芍藥花滿開<br />\n你和我走在相同的路上<br />\n剩下的時間一起度過 每天<br />\n我們之間是比什麼都還閃耀的關係<br />\nLike 100克拉的鑽石<br />\n<br />\n泫雅係咪埋人單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00dd0b2b2cc160ed7b6aa3762eee25cc21f0a37","tid":968234,"uid":223790,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:36:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2247acbe6e525b625c6a4102a73b740808c38283","tid":968234,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:37:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9515b20937ed0ef63be3795dad8f39391c6aadf3","tid":968234,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:37:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb29735524b91ca876fdd9d113b5282df87bec91","tid":968234,"uid":223790,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:39:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec5bdade2d2680ba332feef5122f9b7650ae9a4d","tid":968234,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e24761a591c4d7adf5630dc3a0f96ec0f6c13e5","tid":968234,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"好sweet"},{"pid":"bbdc9da86fc1ba082ac7d511e56909793e9787c2","tid":968234,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:42:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c987155ff1f2cfcf9487ae7bd77440b42b91568","tid":968234,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T06:07:09.000Z","msg":"道友明個樣真係好重白粉味"},{"pid":"7aaafbc82105304d48bb5eabd8682ca0c149a82f","tid":968234,"uid":52073,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T06:09:20.000Z","msg":"泫雅真係好愛條白粉仔 唔通個白粉仔做愛好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f0c992813b497b8a9